This is a node js program where we are creating adhoc server

1. Install the apt-get install nodejs-legacy
2. Execute the application

root@kmaster:/tmp/node.js-recipes# node server.js
Server running at http://0.0.0.0:9000/
Server running at http://0.0.0.0:9001/
Server running at http://0.0.0.0:9002/
Got to the browser try the port 192.168.20.11:9000

